RXE 1
ID app-system-pulse
NAME System Pulse
ICON P
LAYOUT terminal
COLOR 0xFF5DB7A6
INPUT Command:
BUTTON Pulse
USE APPKIT
UI PANEL 0 0 240 36 System Pulse
UI BUTTON 8 8 76 20 Pulse | status
UI BADGE 130 9 82 18 tool
UI OUTPUT 0 46 0 0 Pulse output
DESKTOP 1
DOCK 1
TEXT Runs useful built-in status commands from an app file.
LANG C
CODE lsh("status");
CODE lsh("time");
CODE lsh("fsstat");
